    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> to another plate</p><p>Bash <strong>half</strong> your <strong>crispy onions</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) with a<strong> rolling pin</strong> until finely crushed</p><p>Add the <strong>crushed crispy onions</strong> and <strong>ground paprika </strong>to a separate plate with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your<strong> crispy onion mix</strong></p>",
