      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a chopping board and cover with a sheet of <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Bash the<strong> chicken</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened</p><p>Coat the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> in the<strong> flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add it to the <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and firmly press into the <strong>crispy onion mix </strong>to evenly coat all over</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1701095148707-x200.jpg",
