      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the chicken is nearly cooked, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to the other side of the tray[s] (cooking for 3 or more? Use a separate tray!)</p><p>Return the tray[s]<strong> </strong>to the oven for 2-3 min or until the brioche is warmed through</p>",
