      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burger, top the<strong> brioche base</strong> with a drizzle of the <strong>sweet</strong> <strong>onion gravy</strong>, a <strong>lettuce leaf </strong>and the <strong>crispy onion chicken</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> remaining crispy onions </strong>and the<strong> brioche lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>sage chips</strong>, <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and any <strong>remaining sweet onion gravy</strong> on the side, then drizzle the <strong>salad dressing</strong> over the<strong> </strong>shredded lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
